---
title: Caribbean Pork, Lentil & Veggie Pie with Potato Mash Topping
description: And now for something completely different, meet our game-changing pork & veggie pie! A coconutty, Caribbean-spiced lentil
filling meets a golden potato topping for a dish that's equally wholesome and delish.
